# What We Built

A production-inspired backend system demonstrating:

```text
Data Replication

Circuit Breaker Pattern

Data Recovery Using WAL
```

Built on top of a simple Product API.

Every concept maps directly to what real databases like PostgreSQL and MySQL do internally.

